Class NodeToTriplesMap

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.mem.NodeToTriplesMapBase
org.apache.jena.mem.NodeToTriplesMap
public class NodeToTriplesMap extends NodeToTriplesMapBase
NodeToTriplesMap: a map from nodes to sets of triples. Subclasses must override at least one of useXXXInFilter methods.
